WEBVTT

00:02:26.946 --> 00:02:30.243
qanday davolashni hech kim
tushunmayotgan edi.

00:02:30.243 --> 00:02:33.723
Masalan, sog'ayganlardan qon olib,
uni qayta ishlab,

00:02:33.723 --> 00:02:39.158
plazmasini kasallarga virusdan himoya
sifatida quyishimiz mumkin edi.

00:02:39.158 --> 00:02:41.764
Biroq bu metod biror marta
ham qo'llanilmadi.

00:02:41.764 --> 00:02:43.520
Ko'p ishlar qilinishi mumkin edi.

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:47.415
Aslida bu global masshatbdagi 
muvaffaqiyatsizlik edi.

00:02:48.305 --> 00:02:53.873
JSST epidemiyani kuzatish uchun moliyalash
tirilgan, lekin yuqoridagilar uchun emas.

00:02:55.049 --> 00:02:57.842
Filmlarda odatda hammasi boshqacha.

00:02:57.842 --> 00:03:02.674
Yordamga bir guruh kelishgan
epidemiologlar yuboriladi,